formatted_address: 384 Upper Bukit Timah Rd, The Rail Mall, Singapore 678042
name: Starbucks The Rail Mall @ Fuyong Estate

reviews.text: I have been coming to Starbuck The Rail Mall quite often. I really the place, nice ambiance, good drink, clean place, convenience, friendly and helpful staffs. Thank you to Ella if I remember her name correctly who helped me with drink. I spilled my drink and she help me to make new one that is really made my day and put a smile on my face and she also help me clean up the table. Very nice and kind of her.  Also thank you to her barista team for a great service. I highly recommended! Great service and keep it up!

Staff are really polite, attentive and helpful! Thank you for serving up great coffees to help kickstart my day!

A little cosy Starbucks branch compared to some other outlets.

I today visited Starbucks in railway mall and had an excellent experience thanks to Jonah. Even though the Starbucks app was down and I forgot to bring my physical card to use my rewards, Jonah was incredibly helpful. He tried his best to reboot the app, but unfortunately, we couldn't get it to work and had to purchase the drinks at regular price. Despite this, Jonah's professional and friendly attitude made the situation much more bearable. His dedication to providing great service was truly appreciated. Thank you, Jonah, for your outstanding professionalism!
Nice ambience. Not too crowded at noon time. Located at corner lot ...yuan yang coffee is good, and tiramisu is delicious.
We were well fed and taken care of throughout the dive trip. Service was great. Atmosphere was even better.

vicinity: 384 Upper Bukit Timah Road, The Rail Mall
